        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>analysis and testing techniques [300081683], processes and techniques by specific type [300053003], Processes and Techniques (hierarchy name) [300053001], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
      </Preferred_Parent>
    </Parent_Relationships>
    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Generally, the action or process of determining or calculating a length, quantity, value, magnitude, extent, or other designation of dimensions, size, weight, number, or volume of an object or group of objects, person, animal, plant, plot of land, or other thing, typically by the application of an instrument or device marked in standard units.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000114707/Oxford English Dictionary Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052286/CDWA online (1995-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Generalmente, la acción o el proceso de determinar o de calcular la longitud, la cantidad, el valor, la magnitud, el grado, o la designación de dimensiones, del tamaño, del peso, del número, o del volumen de un objeto o del grupo de los objetos, la persona, el animal, la planta, el diagrama de la tierra, o las cosas, por el uso de un instrumento o de un dispositivo marcado en unidades estándar.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Over het algemeen, de handeling of het proces van het vaststellen of berekenen van een lengte, hoeveelheid, waarde, omvang, mate of andere aanduiding van afmetingen, grootte, gewicht, aantal of volume van een object of groep objecten, persoon, dier, plant, stuk land, of ander ding, door gebruik te maken van een instrument of apparaat dat werkt met standaardeenheden.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099099/Van Dale groot woordenboek (1994)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>泛指利用標有標準單位的儀器或設備， 所進行的測定或計算，測定對象可以是單一或複數物件、人、動物、植物、土地等物，測定或計算內容則包括長度、數量、數值、強度、廣度、尺寸、大小、重量、數量、或容積。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052784/TELDAP database (2009-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
